Package poker.model

This package contains all classes, that are needed to write a new AbstractPlayer for the game.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPlayer
    This abstract class is the basic class for any player that will be available in the game.
    Action
    This class represents an action from a player.
    Card
    This class represents a Card.
    Configuration
    This class holds all registered players and contains methods for the creation of new players.
    Game
    Represents the main game loop.
    GameState
    This class will be the argument for many methods of the AbstractPlayer class.
    MyRandom  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Action.PlayerAction
    This enumeration contains all possible types of an Action: Action.PlayerAction.FOLD Action.PlayerAction.CALL Action.PlayerAction.RAISE
    PlayerState
    This class contains all possible states of a player.

Package poker.model Description

This package contains all classes, that are needed to write a new AbstractPlayer for the game.

Note: You have to create your player in the poker.players package.
Author:
Becker
